{"tid":2365154,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"紀律部隊倡寬免薪俸稅促消費振經濟，有市民反建議紀律部隊用消費券出糧","createTime":"2021-01-13T13:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T08:27:33.000Z","uid":70786,"like":112,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4e952cfe30e574e5184f139a55b748254b2f639d","tid":2365154,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:52:38.000Z","msg":"紀律部隊工會去信陳茂波　促額外寬免薪俸稅「振軍心」稱可刺激消費助經濟復甦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2364936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2364936</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁心繫社會想促進消費？咁不如用消費券出糧啦<br />\n一定促進到經濟，減咩稅姐<br />\n黑警仲可以整個電子消費券添，直接綑綁委任證<br />\n每個黑警份糧部份用消費額形式存入戶口<br />\n每次購物出示委任證就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同叫完雞之後拎張委任證出嚟當俾錢一樣做慣做熟架啦"},{"pid":"a9ff03acd5a2017042c8db57eb43245163fe5d32","tid":2365154,"uid":70786,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"市民有聲音想紀律部隊用消費券出糧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4059c8a1bd16505cfd0dc58f2411cd4a7c849e","tid":2365154,"uid":211466,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"你一出糧洗撚晒佢咪振興經濟囉"},{"pid":"bbcd9f39c6ebaf81f6ae050d8598f0697e86eadf","tid":2365154,"uid":70786,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:56:45.000Z","msg":"拎張委任證出嚟講「我係差人！」<br />\n咁就完成交易<br />\n幾型幾方便呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7521919b96d5fcdea4cd1dea23670fc7a216cd40","tid":2365154,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be4059c8a1bd16505cfd0dc58f2411cd4a7c849e","tid":2365154,"uid":211466,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"你一出糧洗撚晒佢咪振興經濟囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"你估佢地真係想振興經濟咩<br />\n不過佢地既然扮有心<br />\n做市民都好應該成全佢地向政府反映嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5649da2e842b05bd710f03d3114